Package: wmts
Title: Read imagery from WebMap Tile Servers
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Michael", "Sumner", email = "mdsumner@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Read imagery rasters from 'WMTS' ('WebMap Tile Servers') by setting
 a spatial extent.  Zoom level (resolution) is determined automatically for a 
 reasonable sized image at native detail, and can be controlled manually. 
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Imports: 
    slippymath,
    raster,
    spex,
    reproj,
    vapour
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 2.1.0)
